{"id":109543,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/cdc孙静主任：“营养包”有助改善6-56月婴幼儿营养/","date":"2010-09-28T23:42:00Z","modified":"2010-09-28T23:42:00Z","title":"CDC孙静主任：“营养包”有助改善6-56月婴幼儿营养","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><b>HPA</b></span></span><span><b>东亚讯</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><b> </b>  </span><span>8</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>月20</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>日</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>，无国界卫生组织（简称HPA</span></span></span><span>）儿童营养强化培训课程在昆明茶花宾馆四楼会议室举行。中国疾病预防控制中心食品强化办公室主任孙静老师应邀前来授课，并介绍了婴幼儿营养的评价方法以及当前已经开展的婴幼儿辅食营养补充品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>(</span></span><span>即儿童营养包</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>)</span></span><span>的使用情况。<br /></span></p>\n<div><span><a href=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/batch.download.php?aid=292\"><img src=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/attachments/2010/08/24_201008241423191wZyq.thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a></span><span><b><a href=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/batch.download.php?aid=296\"><img src=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/attachments/2010/08/24_2010082414291516Ss5.thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a></b></span></div>\n<div><span><b><span><b><span><b><span><a href=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/batch.download.php?aid=291\"><img src=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/attachments/2010/08/24_201008241422401kNY2.thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a><br /></span></b></span>孙静主任在讲座中</b></span></b></span></div>\n</p>\n<p><span>    “身长和体重是检验婴幼儿健康的最佳方法。”孙静老师表示，选择婴幼儿体重仪时，除了关注质量好坏外，还要关注婴幼儿称体重和量身高的方便性。当前</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>HPA</span></span><span>项目地区使用的测量体重仪器各异，部分地区还沿用当地的古老称重方式，关于这个问题，大家进行了热烈的讨论。</span></p>\n<p><span>此外，孙静老师还介绍了当前在国内开展的婴幼儿营养包项目。该营养包可以补充微量营养素，改善婴幼儿营养不良的状况。当前，山西、四川、青海等省份为贫困地区儿童发放了营养包，而通过营养包干预，中期检验结果显示婴幼儿的营养状况明显好转。</span></p>\n<p><span><span><span>据悉，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>HPA</span></span><span>将开展针对婴幼儿营养改善的相关项目。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>HPA</span></span><span>云南代表处张军主任表示，该讲座对未来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>HPA</span></span><span>的工作有启发性意义，并邀请孙静老师进行深入的交流和指导。</span></span></span></p>\n</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/batch.download.php?aid=293\"><img src=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/attachments/2010/08/24_201008241423421ON8d.thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/batch.download.php?aid=295\"><img src=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/attachments/2010/08/24_201008241426431ZrRh.thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/batch.download.php?aid=294\"><img src=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/attachments/2010/08/24_2010082414253014SB6.thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><b>HPA参会人员认真听讲座</b></span></div>\n</p>\n<p><span><br /></span></p></p>\n","author":138,"categories":[1],"tags":[14483,8771]}